===Etymology===
Literally: the autumn wind sweeps away the fallen leaves
===Idiom===
# to take by storm; to blow away (the competation); to blow out of the water
#: ''[[中国]][[羽球]][[出线]][[无]][[悬念]] [[击败]][[对手]][[如]]“'''秋风扫落叶'''”''[http://72.14.235.104/search?q=cache:xfEKEnQzM9sJ:www.sportsonline.com.cn/GB/channel12/541/5625/5626/20040219/204888.html+%22%E7%A7%8B%E9%A3%8E%E6%89%AB%E8%90%BD%E5%8F%B6%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=44]
#: ''Chinese [[badminton]] team wins hands down, '''blows''' their opponents '''out of the water'''''

